White Raven (Strike)
Level: Crusader 4, Warblade 4
Prerequisite: One White Raven maneuver
Initiation Action: 1 standard action
Range: Melee attack
Target: One creature

The White Raven discipline focuses on tactics, teamwork, and the ability to make an attack that improves your allies' abilities. This strike ruins a foe's defenses. As part of this maneuver, you make a single melee attack. If it hits, you deal an extra 4d6 points of damage, and the target is considered flat-footed until the start of his next turn.
